            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1679312482064-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 1 thin slice[s] per person from your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> and set them aside for serving</p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining tomato</strong> roughly</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat dry with kitchen paper, then remove 1 <strong>outer leaf </strong>per person and set aside until serving</p><p>Tear the <strong>remaining lettuce </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Slice your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into 3 <strong>slices </strong>per person</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1679312489212-x200.jpg",
