            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips have been cooking for 20 min, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>patty[ies]</strong>, press them down firmly with a spatula and cook for 5 min, reduce the heat to medium-high, flip the patty[ies] and cook for a further 2 min or until nicely browned</p><p>Mix most of the <strong>torn lettuce</strong> (save a handful for later!) and <strong>roughly chopped tomato</strong> together – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1679312493625-x200.jpg",
