        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build the burger top your <strong>warmed brioche bun base</strong> with a squeeze of <strong>ketchup</strong>, a <strong>reserved lettuce leaf</strong>, <strong>tomato slices</strong>, a <strong>cheesy patty</strong>, a<strong> roasted onion round </strong>and the<strong> warmed brioche bun lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
